\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc05f20b114fcc28ba004b902295a902de82331","tid":2072800,"uid":158546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T01:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f4605f27de664d0fe8a43313002e5ec9012b956","tid":2072800,"uid":36494,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T01:00:25.000Z","msg":"諗起支那病人係香港私家醫院病房打邊爐<br />\n<br />\n都唔夠印度佬咁癲"},{"pid":"bc7d103cec01c9e5a5c328a2f4ef6e1f6a5012c5","tid":2072800,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T01:24:05.000Z","msg":"咁真係好熱嘛"},{"pid":"9071e3920589af72bdd0844e844f9af58783eb90","tid":2072800,"uid":38651,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6f4605f27de664d0fe8a43313002e5ec9012b956","tid":2072800,"uid":36494,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T01:00:25.000Z","msg":"諗起支那病人係香港私家醫院病房打邊爐<br />\n<br />\n都唔夠印度佬咁癲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T01:55:58.000Z","msg":"打邊爐要插插頭 其實都可以好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426641df66b1e054d816938d5032a3dbfe09a13f","tid":2072800,"uid":335434,"like":144,"dislike":2,"score":142,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:19:06.000Z","msg":"話說某一醫院，出現了一個奇怪的現像，每星期六的六樓的六號病房的六號床位病人在凌晨六點就會去世，護士們都感到人心慌慌，儘量不把病人推到那個床位。<br />\n<br />\n漸漸醫院裡流傳著是醫生的醫術不好的謠言，也謠言那張6號病床有鬼抓人。一日，醫院病房幾乎全滿，護士不得已只好將一位病人推到那個六號床位。<br />\n<br />\n接近凌晨六點時，沒有一個護士敢去巡房，這時醫生為挽回名聲，決定一探究竟！醫生站在病房門口，到六點整時，醫生已害怕的兩腿發麻。<br />\n<br />\n突然６號床的病人，開始痛苦的拉扯窗簾掙扎著，醫生雖然很害怕，但還是鼓起勇氣走近病房...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仔細一看...窗簾外有個穿白衣面無表情的老伯，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老伯將病床旁的氧氣呼吸機插頭拉掉，插上吸塵器的插頭...這是清潔工伯伯每個禮拜的例行打掃工作...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a691fd43c98015381939b820e6f79e5412b52f2","tid":2072800,"uid":176553,"like":88,"dislike":1,"score":87,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rmHTQcx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrmHTQcx.gif&h=cc374dc2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"552be1e88ba0f83197045041e12ff65f8039eef1","tid":2072800,"uid":35696,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:31:59.000Z","msg":"甩左電掣部機應該會響喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c452e53cd96439c32589e85f8071b162d95825","tid":2072800,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />李力持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係笑話寫過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74445a5eda7f26d14829c608d73eeb427a1fed2f","tid":2072800,"uid":230439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:36:11.000Z","msg":"Darwin"},{"pid":"484894736f010971d5f7cc0f9ae87ba050116d3c","tid":2072800,"uid":236171,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:43:57.000Z","msg":"原來個meme真係會發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hXRpWWK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhXRpWWK.jpg&h=aedd388e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d052b95305f43c4a16a22630465d724d7f089b0d","tid":2072800,"uid":185184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:44:21.000Z","msg":"唔知笑好定喊好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3f5916b102052c3275f6d47d8dff2a12cd9f2d","tid":2072800,"uid":11