 href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20111204&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=15860470\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20111204%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D15860470&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduWrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=c6bd6866\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20111204%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D15860470&h=4ef4b403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20111204&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=15860470</a><br />\n<br />\n最經典及令鄧太咋舌的一幕，是其中一名溫州孕婦與丈夫，竟帶備電飯煲在病房內煮臘味飯。他們在洗手間內洗菜洗米，然後在床邊將電飯煲插上電掣，放入臘腸煮飯，「搞到成間房一陣味」。後來她投訴，醫護人員才勸阻他們。<br />\n鄧太表示，入院時院方指四人房爆滿，要求她改住雙人房，幸好她一口拒絕。她於餵奶期間認識入住該雙人房的港媽，該港媽表示，同房的內地孕婦更誇張，竟帶備電鍋與家人在房內打邊爐！「有魚蛋、有菜，三至四個人食」。他們開始打邊爐後不久，該港媽立即投訴，醫護人員隨即制止。"},{"pid":"e2341623deb1dcfac9ec36b1d04e321cbc36ae91","tid":2072800,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"fd0050b8f875e22126684a57c91ea717f2de6e20","tid":2072800,"uid":228143,"like":64,"dislike":5,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T00:45:43.000Z","msg":"其國家都唔信會咁<br />\n<br />\n印度反而信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:42:31.000Z","msg":"印度手足黎，唔好反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc4cc51dbbf418c09d0344fa286d7d08ea733200","tid":2072800,"uid":20018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:46:56.000Z","msg":"仲諗緊點解隔離病房都可以入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c9a7d643fe01ea3de6eacdeaefd69e61e012ea","tid":2072800,"uid":279357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:48:39.000Z","msg":"真係唔知講啲咩好<br />\n真係時間到要報到"},{"pid":"08ca8c04f053b362e75ed117dbbbb84c7c8de6ab","tid":2072800,"uid":202412,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"426641df66b1e054d816938d5032a3dbfe09a13f","tid":2072800,"uid":335434,"like":144,"dislike":2,"score":142,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:19:06.000Z","msg":"話說某一醫院，出現了一個奇怪的現像，每星期六的六樓的六號病房的六號床位病人在凌晨六點就會去世，護士們都感到人心慌慌，儘量不把病人推到那個床位。<br />\n<br />\n漸漸醫院裡流傳著是醫生的醫術不好的謠言，也謠言那張6號病床有鬼抓人。一日，醫院病房幾乎全滿，護士不得已只好將一位病人推到那個六號床位。<br />\n<br />\n接近凌晨六點時，沒有一個護士敢去巡房，這時醫生為挽回名聲，決定一探究竟！醫生站在病房門口，到六點整時，醫生已害怕的兩腿發麻。<br />\n<br />\n突然６號床的病人，開始痛苦的拉扯窗簾掙扎著，醫生雖然很害怕，但還是鼓起勇氣走近病房...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仔細一看...窗簾外有個穿白衣面無表情的老伯，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老伯將病床旁的氧氣呼吸機插頭拉掉，插上吸塵器的插頭...這是清潔工伯伯每個禮拜的例行打掃工作...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:56:40.000Z","msg":"青禾動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e2ad5b9981b200d53617b4fc077b9a14395768","tid":2072800,"uid":292424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:56:53.000Z","msg":"咖哩國<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fc6cad19b97c5c03b074e33ad64a44af13ff27","tid":2072800,"uid":153571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:06:42.000Z","msg":"咁算唔算謀殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418b586d89d2c6f3b6467bed14428c960ce0ecd7","tid":2072800,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05cf7a900d6915a7df4364028eac2fbee94135fe","tid":2072800,"uid":266685,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:19:48.000Z","msg":"CLS 私底下應該深仇大恨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過都聽過有護士話自己以前返工既時候 有個病人部呼吸機個插蘇比另一個病人抆左 原因係部呼吸機嘈住佢瞓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:09:11.000Z","msg":"Cs<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c710d663d7a467396a8376b490960f7cdbf6f7","tid":2072800,"uid":112627,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid